			abstractLg2:
				'The index measures the trend of the income generated by the production sold by farmers at farmgate market prices.',
			prefLabelLg2: 'Agricultural producer price index',
			historyNoteLg2:
				'The IPPAP was successively calculated with a base of 1955, 1970, 1975, 1980, 1990, 1995, 2000 and 2005. It is calculated and disseminated with a base of 2010 since March 2013.',
